gw.api.domain

Interface LineSpecificLocation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BOPLocation, CPLocation, IMLocation

    public interface LineSpecificLocation
    A location that has information that is specific to a particular line of business. This line specific location is backed by a PolicyLocation.
